    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="es">Consumo medido de agua caliente sanitaria. Se expresa como qudt:QuantityValue, típicamente en kWh/m²·año.</rdfs:comment>
    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="en">Measured domestic hot water consumption. Expressed as qudt:QuantityValue, typically in kWh/m²·year.</rdfs:comment>
  </rdf:Description>
